{"word":"πτωχεύω","slug":"πτωχεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πτωχεύω</b></el> <el>(πτωχεύω,) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be a beggar, go begging, beg</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to get by begging</i>, <el>δαῖτα</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to beg</i> or <i>ask an alms of</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}